data.description: Welcome home! New carpet throughout and being installed upstairs soon.  Don't miss seeing this beautifully updated home in West Chester, Ohio 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 half bath. Warm up by the fireplace on chilly nights. Entertain in the private backyard. Enjoy the spacious primary bedroom with huge walk in closet and dressing room. Finished lower level for additional space. No homeowners association! Check it out today!
